        public static java.util.List<InputSet> createInputSetForTaskAndEdges(Node task,
                                                     java.util.List<Edge> edges)
        Creates all new InputSets for a task and a list of edges
        Parameters:
        task - The task which has an input set
        edges - The list of all edges that are part of the fragment the task belongs to (the list has to contain at least all the ingoing associations of the task)
        Returns:
        The newly created InputSets or null if no ingoing (DataFlow)-Associations were found.
